Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认通往密罗奇尼的航线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航线287-56确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8号涡轮加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事吗，克劳德？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把资料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这战舰·卡路纳斯的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛尼奇斯·J·肯尼提督是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球联邦军里\N没人不知道我父亲的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在[雷索尼亚行星之役]中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他巧妙地指挥仅有的7支部队\N打了一场漂亮的胜仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并阻止了躲藏在雷索尼亚联邦政府背后暗中操纵的\N法吉特行星杰·里沃斯大帝的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年仅38岁就晋升为提督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比任何人都尊敬那样的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次我以后备船员的身份\N初次和他坐上同一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且亲眼目睹到他伟大之处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那宽阔的背影中充满了他\N身为地球联邦军提督的威严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为这位英雄肯尼提督的儿子当我感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的任务是到密罗奇尼亚行星进行能量调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近在该行星附近屡次发生原因不明的遇难事故
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就要抵达目标宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离密罗奇尼亚还有20天文单位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航速减为正常速度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御屏障输出功率提到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才抵达密罗奇尼亚的附近时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有探测到这样的小行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底从哪里冒出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分操控装置发生异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,功能恢复需要500秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督，前面出现障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大型的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将与本舰冲撞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于操控装置无法完全操作,来不急回避了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太巨大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种质量，防御屏障无法抵挡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦与本舰冲撞……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰……将全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料上根本没有那样的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标：接近中的大型小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来破坏目标所需要的能量充填\N至少需要250秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以阳电子炮为最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此要暂停正在使用的防御系统\N以及船身控制系统的能量供给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御屏障解除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将全部能量集中到阳电子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船舰承受不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子炮的能量充填65%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机房发生异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子引擎温度异常骤升
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三雷射炮受损
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三区的生命维持机能已经降到三了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子引擎异常高温,已经超过极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船舰会毁掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子炮能量充填完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻破坏前方的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳电子炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人员准备接受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一带的数值又更高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是属于磁能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从性质上的分析来看似乎不是磁能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然非常的相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们继续调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我解除屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得很莽撞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督的判断…我认为非常正确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然的话…我们现在恐怕……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆怯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来让你到宇宙来还是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量测定值是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无法测定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船难事故一定和它脱离不了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有可能是哪个星系的军事设备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里无法取得更进一步的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信它应该能够保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的雷射枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎曾经在内部发生过巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有看过的这种形态的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随意的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会发生什么事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个已经坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快给我退下，不要在那里碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是船上的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分析这样的装置难不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个装置……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传送门，开启
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当世界充满灾祸使人们饱受苦难之时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自异世界的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将手持光之剑为我们消除灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾祸……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您指的就是现在这个世界上所发生的……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不祥的现象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从巨大的陨石落下之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地异变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着就出现了奇形怪状的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个传说所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个勇者可以将我们从苦难中解救出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能像传说中所说的那样就好了……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘到不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看，漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路纳斯…卡路纳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是克劳德·C·肯尼少尉，OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路纳斯，请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是克劳德·肯尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路纳斯 我是克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信器也不行……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊，兔子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有好几年都没有喝到这么好喝的水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…会不会生我的气啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来让你到宇宙来还是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里！ 怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点趁现在逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会被干掉的 你没法跟他打的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来让你到宇宙来还是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆怯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终、终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最危险的时候救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜·蓝佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德·C·肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只剩下这一朵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是我为你摘的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与蕾娜的相遇也正是我冒险的开始
